metadata.name: Henosis Tiger Original #1
metadata.description: This NFT was auctioned on Monday, December 5 as the first piece of the Henosis Tigers by Albert Madaula collection. Henosis Tigers is a fine art collection of hand-drawn felines by internationally acclaimed artist Albert Madaula. He has combined the colors and layers himself to create this one-of-a-kind piece. Only two NFTs in the entire collection are not algorithmically generated and this is one of them. Madaula has also created one physical painting of this piece which was the first NFT to be auctioned from the Henosis Tiger Collection.
